		<segment id="7" parent="14" relname="conjunction">and must be treated accordingly.</segment>
		<segment id="8" parent="16" relname="e-elaboration">Ukrainian counter-terrorism operations are targeted exclusively at illegal armed groups threatening civilians.</segment>
